prompts.frontCover:
Greeting card front cover, comic book art style, flat 2D illustration with bold outlines, halftones, and vibrant, saturated colors. The scene is a dynamic and humorous action sequence on a beautiful, sunny beach with turquoise water and palm trees.

The comic panel depicts the couple from the reference photo, transformed into superhero-style comic characters, in the midst of a playful food fight. Lao Lao, on the left, is mid-laugh as she expertly tosses a perfectly rendered shumai dumpling from a bamboo steamer basket she holds. Jordan, on the right, ducks dramatically with a wide, happy grin, using a large Chinese takeout box as a shield, from which noodles are comically flying out. Around them, other Chinese food items like egg rolls and fluffy bao buns are illustrated mid-air with classic comic book motion lines. The characters' poses are exaggerated and full of energy, and they are wearing the clothing from the photo (Lao Lao in her black puffer jacket, Jordan in his dark grey sweatshirt under the black jacket with a sherpa collar, both without logos).

In the center of the image, contained within a classic comic book burst or speech bubble, is the text "Happy Anniversary, my Super Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, readable, white handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is dynamic, funny, and full of action, capturing a lighthearted and loving moment.
